{"id": "art-490", "label": "Art. 490", "title": "Art. 490: Depunerea recursului", "slug": "art-490", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2015094913\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1221\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2015094913\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 490:\nDepunerea recursului </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1632565008\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1220\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1632565008\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Recursul &#351;i, dac&#259; este cazul, motivele de\ncasare se depun la instan&#355;a a c&#259;rei hot&#259;râre se atac&#259;, sub\nsanc&#355;iunea nulit&#259;&#355;ii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1263343707\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1219\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:titl